a | ma|zal|i y|oki| pe|ngo|ali|pe |so |nso|oto|ons| ba|ala|mot|a k|eng|nyo|eko|o e|nge|yon| ny|kol|lik|iko|a e|o y|ang|ye | ye|oko|ma |o a|go | ek|ko |e m|aza|te |olo|sal|ama|si | az|mak|e b|lo | te|ta |isa|ako|amb|sen|ong|e n|ela|oyo|i k|ani| es|o m|ni |osa| to|ban|bat|a t|mba|ing|yo | oy|eli|a p|mbo|o p|mi | mi| nd|ba |i m|bok|i p|isi|mok|lis|nga|ge |nde|koz|bo |gel|ato|o t|mos|aka|oba|ese|lam|kop| ez|lon|den|omb|o b|ota|sa |ga |e a|e y|eza|kos|lin|esa|e e|kob|e k|sam|kot|kan|bot|ika|ngi|kam|ka | po|gom|oli|ope|yan|elo| lo|ata| el|bon|oka|po |bik|ate| bi|a s|i t|i b|omi|pes|wa | se|oza|lok|bom|oke|som|zwa|mis|i e|bek|iki| at|ola|ti |ozw|lib|o l|osu|oso|e t|nda|ase|ele|kel|omo|bos|su |usu|sus|bal|i l|ami|o o|bak| nz|pon|tel|mob|mu | ep|nza|asi|mbi|ati|kat|le |gi |ana|oti|ndi|tan|a o|wan|obe|kum|nya|mab|bis|nis|opo|tal|mat| ka|bol|and|aye|baz|u y|eta| ta|ne |ene|emb|sem|e l|gis|ben| ak| en|mal|obo|gob|ike|se |ibo|’te| ’t|umb| so|mik|oku|be |mbe|bi |i a|eni|i o| mb|tey|san| et|abo|ebe|geb|eba|yeb|bu | as|ote|sik|ema|eya|ibe|mib|ai |pai|mwa|kes|da |may|boz|amu|a a|kom|mel|ona|ebi|ia |ina|tin| ti|bwa|sol|son",som:" ka|ka |ay |uu |an |yo |oo |aan|aha| wa|da | qo| in| u |sha| xa|a i|ada|iyo| iy|ma |ama| ah| la|qof|aa |hay|ga |a a|a w|ah | dh|a s| da|in |xaq| oo|a d|aad|yah|eey| le|isa|lee|u l|q u|aq | si|taa|eya|ast|la |of |iya|sa |y i|u x|sta|kas|xuu|uxu|wux| wu|iis|nuu|inu|ro | am| ma|a q|wax|dha|ala|kal|nay|f k|a k|le |ku | ku| sh|o i|a l|ta |maa|a u|dii|loo| lo|o a|ale|ara|ana|iga|o d| uu|ha |lo |o m|o x|doo|aro|kar|yaa|gu |si |ima|na | xo| fa|adk|do |a x|ad |aas| qa| so|a o| ba|lag| aa| he|dka|adi|soo|o k|aqa| is|ash|u d|had| ga|eed|san|u k|a m|iin|i k| ca|u s|n l|yad|rka|axa|elo|hel|aga|hii|o h|o q| ha|id |n k| mi|baa| xu|har|xor|aar|ax |mad|add|nta|mid|aal|waa|haa|ina|qaa|daa|agu|ark|o w|nka|u h|dad|ihi| bu| ho|naa|n a|ays|haq|a h|o l| gu|o s|aya|saa|lka| ee| sa|dda|ab |nim|quu|gga|ank|kii|rci|arc|n s|a g| ji|gel| ge|eli|ysa|a f|siy|int|laa|uuq|uqu|xuq| mu|i a|uur